title: 2D Low-Poly Christmas Pack - 100 Icons with Transparent Background
description: Elevate your holiday game with our 2D Low-Poly Christmas Pack!
longDescription:
Elevate your holiday game with our 2D Low-Poly Christmas Pack! This delightful asset includes 100 charming Christmas icons, each meticulously crafted in a low-poly style with a transparent background. Perfect for adding a festive touch to your game or project.


Key Features:


100 unique low-poly Christmas icons

Transparent background for seamless integration

High-quality PNG format

Resolution: 500 x 500 pixels

Versatility for Your Projects:

Whether you're working on a casual mobile game, a festive interactive website,

or a cozy winter-themed application, these icons will bring a touch of holiday 

magic to your project. Easily customize and integrate them into various genres, 

from casual to RPG, enhancing the visual appeal and holiday spirit.


User-Friendly Integration:

With a user-friendly resolution of 500 x 500 pixels and a transparent background,

 incorporating these icons into your project is a breeze. 

Effortlessly drag and drop them into your scenes, UI, 

or promotional materials to instantly elevate the festive atmosphere.


Continuous Support and Updates:

This is the first version of our Christmas Pack, 

and we're committed to providing ongoing support and updates. 

Your feedback is valuable, and we encourage you to leave reviews and ratings. Expect regular updates with more festive additions to keep your content fresh and exciting.


Get in Touch:

Have questions, suggestions, or need assistance? Feel free to reach out to us at 

tanava72@gmail.com. We value your input and are here to ensure your holiday project shines bright!


Transform your project into a winter wonderland with the 2D Low-Poly Christmas Pack.

Download now and let the holiday joy begin!
